---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Tangem Pay Review 2026: Hardware Wallet Crypto Card | GetNoKYC">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a> → 
      <a href="/reviews/" class="hover:text-white">Reviews</a> → Tangem Pay
    </nav>

    <header class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
        <span class="badge badge-verified">SECURE</span>
        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Updated: February 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Tangem Pay Review 2026: Hardware Wallet Meets Debit Card</h1>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm">
        <span class="text-yellow-500">★★★★½ 4.5/5</span>
        <span class="text-gray-400">42 Countries</span>
        <span class="text-emerald-500">Hardware Security</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] rounded-xl p-6 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4">Quick Facts</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Card Network</span><p class="font-medium">Visa</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">No-KYC Limit</span><p class="font-medium">€150/month</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Setup Cost</span><p class="font-medium">€54.90</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Security</span><p class="font-medium text-emerald-500">Hardware chip</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Top-up</span><p class="font-medium text-emerald-500">0%</p></div>
        <div><span class="text-gray-500">Crypto</span><p class="font-medium">USDC</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h2>What is Tangem Pay?</h2>
      <p>Tangem Pay combines a <strong>hardware wallet with a Visa debit card</strong>. Your private keys never leave the physical card chip — similar to a Ledger or Trezor, but in a credit card form factor.</p>

      <h2>No-KYC Tier</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Max Balance:</strong> €150</li>
        <li><strong>Monthly Limit:</strong> €150</li>
        <li><strong>Requirements:</strong> Email + phone</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Pros</h2>
      <ul class="text-emerald-400">
        <li>✅ <strong>True Hardware Security</strong> — Keys never leave the chip</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>42 Countries</strong> — Wider availability than EU-only options</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>Zero Top-up Fees</strong> — On-chain USDC spending</li>
        <li>✅ <strong>No Seed Phrase</strong> — Can't be stolen remotely</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Cons</h2>
      <ul class="text-red-400">
        <li>❌ <strong>€54.90 Setup</strong> — Higher initial cost</li>
        <li>❌ <strong>Physical Card Required</strong> — No virtual option</li>
        <li>❌ <strong>USDC Only</strong> — Limited crypto support</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Verdict</h2>
      <p><strong>Best for security-focused users</strong> who want hardware wallet protection. The €54.90 cost is worth it if you value not-your-keys-not-your-coins philosophy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <a href="https://tangem.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-cta">Get Tangem Pay →</a>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-4">Affiliate link.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
      <a href="/" class="text-emerald-500 hover:underline">← Back to all cards</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: white; }
  .prose p { color: #d1d5db; margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .prose ul { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .prose li { color: #d1d5db; }
</style>
